title.rendered: Tesla Model S by Prestige Motorcars

content.rendered:
Model S sets an industry standard for performance and safety. Tesla’s all-electric powertrain delivers unparalleled performance in all weather conditions – with Dual Motor All-Wheel Drive, adaptive air suspension and ludicrous acceleration. It is built with best in class storage, seating for up to five adults and an expansive 17-inch touchscreen. Advanced noise engineering creates sound dynamics comparable to a recording studio, while the standard Glass Roof provides a spacious interior experience for every passenger. / Model S menetapkan standar mumpuni untuk kinerja dan keselamatan. Semua powertrain listrik Tesla memiliki kinerja tak tertandingi dalam segala cuaca. Dilengkapi Dual Motor All-Wheel Drive, suspensi udara adaptif, dan akselerasi menggelitik adrenalin. Desain kabin mobil yang lega, apik dan juara di kelasnya. Berkapasitas lima orang dewasa, layar sentuh 17 inci dan interior Atap Kaca memberi kesan luas bagi setiap penumpang. Sudah terpasang rekayasa kebisingan guna menciptakan dinamika suara sebanding dengan studio.
